dct_title_s: Carte de la Baye de Saldana ou Saldane
dct_alternative_sm: [Histoire générale des voyages] Tom. V. No. 4
dct_description_sm: Dressée sur les Remarques des Navigateurs, Par N. B. Ingr. de la Marine.
Pictorial relief; depths shown by soundings.
Bar scale: "Lieues Marines de France et d'Angleterre."
On coast of northern bay: "Cette Coste n'est pas connue."
Shows coastal relief, islands, low water areas/sand banks, places to anchor.
List of "Remarques" describing three known water sources (A-C) and the absence of woods.
From "Histoire générale des voyages," published by Didot, date unknown.
